description: Tender beef tenderloin wrapped in flaky puff pastry, served with a rich mushroom duxelles.
Fresh mozzarella balls, cherry tomatoes, and basil leaves drizzled with balsamic glaze.
Succulent roasted salmon fillet topped with a creamy dill sauce, served with asparagus.
Layers of pasta, ricotta cheese, and a medley of roasted vegetables in a hearty tomato sauce.
Warm chocolate cake with a molten chocolate center, served with vanilla ice cream.
Delicate pastry crust filled with pastry cream and topped with fresh seasonal fruits.
Creamy blend of spinach, artichoke hearts, and cheeses, served with toasted baguette slices.
Grilled chicken breast served on a bed of romaine lettuce with parmesan cheese, croutons, and Caesar dressing.
Tangy and sweet lemon bars with a shortbread crust.
Rich and fudgy chocolate brownies made with gluten-free flour.
